@startuml AdminSec_UC02-40_Consulter_Rapports
title UC-02-40: Consulter Rapports - AdminSecretariat (Tous Scenarios)

actor AdminSecretariat as A
participant Dashboard
participant Systeme
participant DB
participant Logs

A -> Dashboard: 1. Accede a Rapports
activate Dashboard

Dashboard -> DB: 2. Recupere types rapports disponibles (verifier secretariat_id)
activate DB

alt Erreur BD
  DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: BD indisponible
  deactivate DB
  Dashboard --> A: ERREUR 500: Impossible charger rapports
  deactivate Dashboard
else BD disponible
  DB --> Dashboard: Retourne rapports (facturation, paies, conformite)
  deactivate DB

  Dashboard --> A: 3. Affiche menu rapports
  deactivate Dashboard

  A -> Dashboard: 4. Clique Rapport Facturation
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard --> A: 5. Affiche formulaire filtres (periode, detail)
  deactivate Dashboard

  A -> Dashboard: 6. Selectionne periode et clique Generer
  activate Dashboard

  Dashboard -> Systeme: 7. Valide parametres rapport (periode valide, range acceptables)
  activate Systeme

  alt Parametres invalides
    Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Parametres invalides
    deactivate Systeme
    Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Periode ou filtres invalides
    deactivate Dashboard
  else Parametres valides
    deactivate Systeme

    Dashboard -> DB: 8. Recupere donnees factures periode (verifier secretariat_id)
    activate DB

    alt Erreur BD
      DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Donnees indisponibles
      deactivate DB
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Impossible charger donnees facturation
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Donnees OK
      DB --> Dashboard: Retourne factures (montants, dates, clients)
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> Systeme: 9. Agrege donnees et genere statistiques rapport
      activate Systeme

      Systeme -> Systeme: 10. Calcule KPIs (total, par client, TTC/HT)

      Systeme --> Dashboard: Rapport genere (donnees + graphiques)
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> DB: 11. Enregistre log audit: Consultation rapport facturation (timestamp, secretariat_id)
      activate DB
      DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
      deactivate DB

      Dashboard -> Logs: 12. Log event: Rapport facturation consulte
      activate Logs
      Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
      deactivate Logs

      Dashboard --> A: 13. Affiche rapport avec graphiques et tableaux
      deactivate Dashboard

      A -> Dashboard: 14. Clique Telecharger Rapport
      activate Dashboard

      Dashboard --> A: 15. PDF rapport telecharge
      deactivate Dashboard

      note over A, Logs
        **RAPPORT FACTURATION OK:**
        - Donnees agrege OK
        - Graphiques generes
        - PDF telechargeable
        - Acces loggue
      end note
    end

    A -> Dashboard: 16. Clique Rapport Paies
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard --> A: 17. Affiche formulaire filtres (consultant, client, periode)
    deactivate Dashboard

    A -> Dashboard: 18. Selectionne consultant et periode et clique Generer
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 19. Valide parametres rapport
    activate Systeme

    alt Parametres invalides
      Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Parametres invalides
      deactivate Systeme
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Periode ou consultant invalide
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Parametres valides
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> DB: 20. Recupere fiches paie (verifier secretariat_id et consultant appartient au secretariat)
      activate DB

      alt Consultant inexistant OU n'appartient pas au secretariat OU erreur BD
        DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR 404 ou 403 ou 500: Non trouve, acces refuse, ou BD down
        deactivate DB
        Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Consultant inexistant, acces refuse, ou service indisponible
        deactivate Dashboard
      else Fiches paie OK
        DB --> Dashboard: Retourne fiches paie (nb, montants, clients)
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> Systeme: 21. Analyse performance paies (delais, corrections, anomalies)
        activate Systeme

        Systeme -> Systeme: 22. Calcule KPIs paies (nb fiches, delais, taux correction)

        Systeme --> Dashboard: Rapport genere
        deactivate Systeme

        Dashboard -> DB: 23. Enregistre log audit: Consultation rapport paies (admin, consultant, timestamp, secretariat_id)
        activate DB
        DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> Logs: 24. Log event: Rapport paies consulte
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
        deactivate Logs

        Dashboard --> A: 25. Affiche rapport paies avec statistiques consultant
        deactivate Dashboard

        A -> Dashboard: 26. Clique Telecharger Rapport
        activate Dashboard

        Dashboard --> A: 27. PDF rapport telecharge
        deactivate Dashboard

        note over A, Logs
          **RAPPORT PAIES OK:**
          - Donnees consultant recuperees
          - KPIs calcules
          - PDF telechargeable
          - Isolation donnees verifiee
          - Acces loggue
        end note
      end
    end

    A -> Dashboard: 28. Clique Rapport Conformite
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard --> A: 29. Affiche formulaire filtres (type: ONSS, DIMONA, etc., periode)
    deactivate Dashboard

    A -> Dashboard: 30. Selectionne periode et type et clique Generer
    activate Dashboard

    Dashboard -> Systeme: 31. Valide parametres rapport
    activate Systeme

    alt Parametres invalides
      Systeme --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Parametres invalides
      deactivate Systeme
      Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Periode ou type conformite invalide
      deactivate Dashboard
    else Parametres valides
      deactivate Systeme

      Dashboard -> DB: 32. Recupere declarations ONSS/DIMONA (verifier secretariat_id)
      activate DB

      alt Erreur BD
        DB --> Dashboard: ERREUR: Donnees indisponibles
        deactivate DB
        Dashboard --> A: ERREUR: Impossible charger donnees conformite
        deactivate Dashboard
      else Donnees OK
        DB --> Dashboard: Retourne declarations (ONSS, DIMONA, metadata)
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> Systeme: 33. Analyse conformite et detecte anomalies
        activate Systeme

        Systeme -> Systeme: 34. Valide declarations et calcule conformite %

        Systeme --> Dashboard: Rapport genere avec alertes si anomalies
        deactivate Systeme

        Dashboard -> DB: 35. Enregistre log audit: Consultation rapport conformite (timestamp, secretariat_id)
        activate DB
        DB --> Dashboard: Audit log enregistre en BD
        deactivate DB

        Dashboard -> Logs: 36. Log event: Rapport conformite consulte
        activate Logs
        Logs --> Dashboard: Event loggue pour monitoring
        deactivate Logs

        Dashboard --> A: 37. Affiche rapport conformite avec alertes si besoin
        deactivate Dashboard

        A -> Dashboard: 38. Clique Telecharger Rapport
        activate Dashboard

        Dashboard --> A: 39. PDF rapport telecharge
        deactivate Dashboard

        note over A, Logs
          **RAPPORT CONFORMITE OK:**
          - Declarations recuperees OK
          - Conformite analysee
          - Alertes si anomalies
          - PDF telechargeable
          - Acces loggue
        end note
      end
    end
  end
end

@enduml
